%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20avian%20influenza%20A%20H5N1%20virion%2C%20viewed%20through%20an%20electron%20microscope.%3Cp%3ECynthia%20Goldsmith%2C%20Jackie%20Katz%2FCDC%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20pigs%20are%20infected%2C%20the%20greater%20this%20risk%20is.%20However%2C%20Schultz-Cherry%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20would%20not%20need%20to%20see%20pig-to-pig%20transmission%20to%20worry%20about%20this%20mixing%20vessel%20or%20this%20mixing%20bowl%20effect.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20other%20animal%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list%26quot%3B%20with%20pigs%2C%20Richard%20Webby%2C%20a%20virologist%20at%20St.%20Jude%20and%20director%20of%20the%20WHO%20animal%20and%20bird%20flu%20center%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20June.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20just%20be%20due%20to%20gaps%20in%20our%20understanding%20of%20animal%20influenza.%20After%20all%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20would%20have%20told%20you%20that%20cows%20don't%20get%20flu.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a4f46f3-5945-4643-8803-01a4a97b4066%5C%22%3EBad%20timing%3A%20Flu%20season%20is%20in%20full%20swing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20timing%20of%20this%20development%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20ideal%2C%26quot%3B%20Schultz-Cherry%20said%2C%20because%20it's%20the%20middle%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftell-which-virus-you-have-flu-covid-rsv-symptoms-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflu%20season%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20pigs%20can%20get%20the%20strains%20of%20flu%20that%20circulate%20among%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20season's%20flu%20strains%20were%20to%20overlap%20with%20a%20pig%20H5N1%20infection%2C%20that%20would%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20gene-swapping%20that%20helps%20the%20bird%20flu%20adapt%20to%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReally%20it%20would%20just%20take%20one%20pig%2C%26quot%3B%20Schultz-Cherry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGettin