and%20the%20latex%20layer%20provides%20a%20cozy%20feeling%20and%20pressure%20relief%2C%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20coils%20support%20my%20hips%20and%20lower%20back%20and%20keep%20my%20spine%20aligned.%20I%20never%20once%20woke%20up%20with%20pain%20or%20soreness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20combination%20sleeper%2C%20so%20I%20like%20sleeping%20on%20my%20stomach%2C%20back%2C%20and%20sides.%20When%20it%20came%20to%20sleeping%20on%20the%20Awara%20Premier%20Luxury%20Hybrid%20Mattress%2C%20I%20found%20that%20sleeping%20on%20my%20stomach%20and%20back%20was%20most%20comfortable.%20That's%20not%20to%20say%20that%20I%20couldn't%20sleep%20on%20my%20side%20on%20this%20mattress%2C%20only%20that%20it%20didn't%20feel%20as%20natural%20as%20the%20other%20two%20sleep%20positions.%20When%20I%20measured%20the%20deviation%20angle%20of%20the%20mattress%20while%20lying%20on%20my%20side%2C%20it%20came%20out%20to%20six%20degrees.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20the%20mattress%20needs%20a%20bit%20more%20give%20to%20make%20sleeping%20on%20my%20side%20more%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22spinal%20alignment%20test%20on%20a%20woman%2C%20measures%206%20degrees%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671a99899b3250dbbce9e155%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20lying%20on%20my%20side%2C%20the%20mattress%20did%20a%20good%20job%20of%20keeping%20my%20spine%20aligned%2C%20but%20strict%20side%20sleepers%20may%20need%20something%20more%20pressure-relieving.%20%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20I'd%20label%20this%20mattress%20medium%20or%20a%206%20out%20of%2010%20on%20the%20firmness%20scale.%20It's%20definitely%20on%20the%20softer%20end%20of%20mattresses%20that%20are%20designed%20for%20stomach%20and%20back%20sleepers%2C%20but%20that%20makes%20it%20a%20better%20sell%2C%20in%20my%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d18fa75d-a69c-4452-93a5-a1f28101fc37%5C%22%3EHeat%20dissipation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Awara%20Premier%20Luxury%20Hybrid%20Mattress%20does%20a%20great%20job%20at%20dispersing%20heat%2C%20which%20is%20not%20surprising%20considering%20that%20hybrid%20mattresses%20result%20in%20better%20airflow.%20Plus%2C%20it's%20outfitted%20with%20a%20cover%20that%20has%20wool%20which%20wicks%20moisture%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20a%20naturally%20hot%20sleeper%2C%20but%20I've%20tested%20plenty%20of%20mattresses%20that%20retain%20heat%2C%20and%20it%20was%20clear%20the%20Awara%20Premier%20Luxury%20Hybrid%20Mattress%20does%20not%20do%20that.%20Though%20the%20mattress%20is%20not%20cool%20to%20the%20touch%2C%20it%20did%20a%20great%20job%20of%20keeping%20me%20neutral%20%E2%80%94%20temperature-wise%20%E2%80%94%20throughout%20the%20night.%20I%20never%20woke%20up%20sweating%20or%20warm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20used%20an%20infrared%20thermometer%20to%20take%20temperature%20readings%20of%20the%20Awara%20Premier%20Luxury%20Hybrid%20Mattress.%20On%20average%2C%20the%20mattress%20is%2081.5%20degrees%20Fahrenheit.%20After%20lying%20down%2C%20it%20had%20an%2085-degree%20temperature%20reading.%20Two%20minutes%20after%20getting%20up%2C%20it%20dropped%20to%2082%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2293812ab8-dfdc-4f6e-8c53-2d1801eb5022%5C%22%3EEdge%20support%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20side%20shot%20of%20the%20awara%20mattress%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671a9880a0a0cc14f223b0e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAwara%20mattresses%20have%20gauge%20edge%20support%20perimeter%20coils%20to%20reinforce%20the%20edges.%20The%20sides%20offer%20the%20most%20security%20while%20sitting%20at%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20bed%20caused%20more%20sinkage.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20brand%2C%20the%20Awara%20Premier%20Luxury%20Hybrid%20Mattress%20has%20thick%20gauge%20edge%20support%20perimeter%20coils%20to%20assist%20in%20edge%20support.%20To%20see%20how%20supportive%20these%20reinforced%20coils%20were%2C%20I%20ran%20tests%20along%20the%20sides%20and%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20mattress.%20When%20I%20sat%20on%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20mattress%2C%20I%20sunk%204%20inches.%20However%2C%20I%20sunk%206%20inches%20when%20sitting%20at%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20support%20along%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20mattress%20and%20how%20I%20could%20easily%20put%20on%20my%20shoes%2C%20get%20dressed%2C%20and%20stand%20up.%20That%20said%2C%20I%20found%20that%20the%20corners%20of%20the%20mattress%20and%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20bed%20were%20noticeably%20less%20supportive.%20It's%20unlikely%20you'll%20sit%20on%20the%20corners%2C%20but%20I%20would%20advise%20using%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20mattress%20rather%20than%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20bed%20to%20get%20dressed%2C%20as%20the%20sides%20are%20more%20supportive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20not%20a%20moment%20when%20I%20thought%20I%20might%20slip%20or%20roll%20off%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20bed%20when%20lying%20near%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20mattress.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20could%20lie%20on%20my%20side%20at%20a%2090-degree%20angle%20on%20the%20very%20edge%20of%20the%20mattress%20without%20falling%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c1e2621f-8a03-49ef-a1ee-ea4c19434c6e%5C%22%3EMotion%20isolation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThose%20who%20share%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20partner%20should%20invest%20in%20a%20mattress%20with%20great%20motion%20isolation%20capabilities.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20you%20want%20a%20mattress%20that%20can%20isolate%20the%20motion%20of%20your%20fidgety%20partner%20or%20pet%20which%20will%20prevent%20you%20from%20feeling%20their%20movements%20and%20thus%20waking%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20tested%20the%20motion%20isolation%20of%20this%20mattress%20in%20a%20number%20of%20ways.%20First%2C%20I%20had%20another%20person%20get%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20bed%20and%20change%20sleep%20positions%20while%20lying%20on%20the%20bed.%20While%20I%20did%20feel%20some%20of%20their%20movements%2C%20I%20didn't%20feel%20them%20all.%20From%20this%20test%20alone%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20the%20motion%20isolation%20was%20a%207.5%20on%20a%2010-point%20scale%20(with%2010%20being%20perfect%20and%201%20indicating%20poor%20motion%20isolation).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20second%20test%20involved%20placing%20an%20unopened%20soda%20can%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20mattress%20and%20dropping%20a%2015-lb.%20dumbbell%20five%20times%20at%20a%20height%20of%20four%20feet%20and%20a%20distance%20of%2012%20inches%20from%20the%20can.%20As%20I%20did%20this%2C%20I%20had%20the%20Vibrometer%20app%20running%20on%20my%20phone%2C%20which%20was%20placed%20on%20the%20mattress%20about%2012%20inches%20from%20the%20can.%20Not%20only%20did%20the%20can%20fall%20each%20time%2C%20but%20according%20to%20the%20app%2C%20the%20average%20vibration%20reading%20was%20a%204.5%20or%20%26quot%3Bmoderate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20translate%20those%20readings%20for%20you%2C%20but%20I%20can%20say%20that%20I%20ran%20this%20same%20test%20on%20two%20other%20mattresses%20in%20my%20home%20(both%20of%20which%20are%20organic%20latex%20mattresses)%2C%20and%20the%20results%20were%20about%20the%20same.%20I'm%20inclined%20to%20say%20that%20if%20you%20did%20this%20test%20on%20most%20mattresses%2C%20you'll%20likely%20see%20the%20can%20tip%20over%2C%20but%20perhaps%20the%20vibration%20readings%20will%20differ.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOverall%2C%20I%20would%20say%20that%20the%20Awara%20Premier%20Luxury%20Hybrid%20Mattress%20does%20a%20good%20%E2%80%94%20though%20not%20great%20%E2%80%94%20job%20of%20motion%20isolation.%20If%20you're%20very%20sensitive%20to%20movement%2C%20it%20may%20not%20be%20a%20fit%20for%20you%3B%20however%2C%20for%20the%20average%20sleeper%2C%20it'll%20do%20the%20trick.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b01e668-6d7f-4c87-906a-5ff71a214dbb%5C%22%3ETrial%20period%20and%20warranty%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAwara%20offers%20one%20of%20the%20best%20trial%20periods%20and%20warranties%20on%20the%20mattress%20market.%20You%20can%20test%20the%20mattress%20for%20365%20nights%2C%20and%20you'll%20get%20a%20full%20refund%20if%20you%20return%20it%20within%20that%20time%20period.%20Note%20that%20Awara%20suggests%20sleeping%20on%20the%20mattress%20for%2030%20days%20before%20returning%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAwara%20offers%20a%20Forever%20(or%20lifetime)%20Warranty%20to%20the%20original%20purchaser%20(you%20must%20keep%20your%20receipt%20for%20proof%20of%20purchase)%20of%20the%20mattress.%20Their%20warranty%20terms%20are%20pretty%20standard.%20For%20instance%2C%20you%20can%20use%20the%20warranty%20if%20there%20is%20an%20invisible%20indentation%20of%20more%20than%201.5%20inches%20or%20some%20other%20physical%20flaw%20or%20manufacturing%20defect.%20In%20the%20first%2010%20years%2C%20Awara%20will%20replace%20your%20mattress%20with%20a%20new%20one%20at%20no%20charge.%20After%2010%20years%2C%20Awara%20will%20repair%20or%20replace%20the%20mattress%2C%20however%2C%20you'll%20be%20charged%20a%20%2450%20shipping%20fee%20each%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22082d2ef1-41d8-41c8-b912-5821d154ad3f%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECompared%20to%20some%20mattresses%20on%20the%20market%2C%20there%20aren't%20a%20lot%20of%20customization%20options%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20ordering%20this%20Awara%20mattress.%20You%20can't%20choose%20a%20firmness%20level%2C%20add%20a%20pillowtop%2C%20or%20determine%20the%20height%20of%20the%20mattress.%20It's%20not%20the%20biggest%20drawback%2C%20especially%20considering%20how%20comfortable%20this%20mattress%20is%2C%20and%20how%20well%20it%20does%20in%20terms%20of%20temperature%20regulation%2C%20but%20it's%20something%20to%20note.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20only%20notable%20con%20is%20that%20the%20edge%20support%20along%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20mattress%20is%20lacking.%20It's%20not%20as%20supportive%20or%20as%20reinforced%20as%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20Awara.%20Again%2C%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20sit%20on%20or%20lie%20near%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20mattress%20rather%20than%20at%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20bed%2C%20so%20I%20wouldn't%20let%20this%20downside%20dissuade%20you%20from%20buying%20this%20mattress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b91057ca-5c6c-4273-b867-2fc419761cce%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20could%20always%20go%20with%20the%20base%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56307-20%26h%3Df623989faf9e1b76c75c6cacb45db87ca190f48e0cdd3c8f331c2265d2c532e5%26postID%3D671a9542434c477c2340ae4e%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fawara-premier-luxury-hybrid-mattress-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.awarasleep.com%252Fmattress%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Awara%20Natural%20Luxury%20Hybrid%20Mattress%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20only%20major%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20is%20that%20the%20Premier%20has%20a%20four-inch%20layer%20of%20organic%20latex%20compared%20to%20the%20two-inch%20latex%20layer%20of%20the%20Natural%20Luxury%20Hybrid.%20That%20said%2C%20I'm%20not%20sure%20the%20additional%20two%20inches%20are%20worth%20an%20extra%20%24430%20over%20the%20%241%2C000%20value%20play%20of%20Awara's%20base%20offering.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56307-20%26h%3D57bd9e924b53ce8c9b01bb6378e268e01f36af2d76cc19902480abed04b95c65%26postID%3D671a9542434c477c2340ae4e%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252F