a%20private%20message%20board%20for%20Microsoft%20employees%20that's%20run%20by%20Blind.%20This%20platform%20requires%20staff%20to%20provide%20an%20official%20verified%20company%20email%20before%20being%20allowed%20to%20join.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20new%20Copilot%20is%20a%20step%20backward%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20person%20wrote%20in%20the%20Microsoft%20group%20on%20Blind%2C%20according%20to%20screenshots%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20new%20Copilot%20update%20is%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239a19154-a560-4e0d-845a-4392418cb652%5C%22%3EApp%20Store%20reviews%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20comments%20are%20supported%20by%20public%20reviews%20of%20the%20Copilot%20app%20on%20Apple's%20App%20Store.%20Until%20this%20latest%20update%2C%20the%20product%20had%20largely%20favorable%20reviews%2C%20with%20an%20average%20of%204.8%20stars%20out%20of%205%20based%20on%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20ratings.%20But%20since%20the%20Oct.%201%20refresh%2C%20the%20reviews%20have%20taken%20a%20negative%20turn%2C%20garnering%20more%20than%20250%20one-star%20reviews%20this%20month.%20That%20compares%20to%20only%20about%2020%20one-star%20ratings%20in%20September%20before%20the%20update.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20so%20good%20before%20updating%20to%20this%20version%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20reviewer%20wrote.%20Another%20said%20the%20Copilot%20app%20is%20%26quot%3Bdumbed%20down%20and%20less%20functional.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20release%20such%20an%20amazing%20app%20and%20then%20update%20it%20to%20what%20it%20is%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20a%20third%20reviewer%20wrote%20in%20the%20App%20Store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226b780fe7-e462-4af4-8d5f-a289a283454b%5C%22%3EHigh%20expectations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-hired-inflection-team-amid-board-concerns-about-openai-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehired%20Suleyman%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%20to%20oversee%20consumer%20AI%20products%20such%20as%20the%20Bing%20search%20engine%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcopilot.microsoft.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECopilot%20AI%20chatbot%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20the%20cofounder%20of%20AI%20pioneer%20DeepMind%2C%20there%20were%20high%20expectations%20for%20Suleyman's%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20just%20one%20of%20many%20projects%20he's%20working%20on%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20issues%20may%20be%20somewhat%20out%20of%20his%20control.%20New%20product%20updates%20can%20also%20suffer%20from%20early%20teething%20problems%20that%20can%20sometimes%20be%20ironed%20out%20later.%20Some%20users%20also%20react%20negatively%20when%20an%20app%20they've%20gotten%20used%20to%20suddenly%20changes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20new%20Copilot%20consumer%20app%20represents%20a%20fundamental%20shift%2C%20evolving%20from%20a%20transactional%20tool%20to%20a%20companion%20experience%20that%20is%20more%20conversational%2C%20where%20it's%20there%20to%20support%20you%2C%20guide%20you%20and%20help%20you%20solve%20less%20defined%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20Divya%20Kumar%2C%20general%20manager%20of%20Copilot%20and%20AI%20marketing%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20add%20new%20features%20and%20functionality%20as%20we%20continue%20to%20listen%20to%20and%20address%20our%20customers'%20feedback%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229fae3a1e-ecfc-40c8-8572-54a76c5d410c%5C%22%3EMultiple%20Copilots%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Microsoft%20employee%20message%20board%20on%20Blind%2C%20some%20people%20compared%20the%20updated%20Copilot%20app%20for%20consumers%20to%20a%20different%20Copilot%20tool%20that's%20designed%20for%20corporate%20customers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20has%20many%20versions%20of%20its%20Copilots.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20that%20one%20Microsoft%20executive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-customers-complain-copilot-doesnt-work-as-well-as-chatgpt-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20company%20is%20struggling%20to%20educate%20customers%20on%20the%20differences%20between%20the%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Suleyman's%20consumer%20Copilot%20app%20is%20separate%20from%20an%20AI%20Copilot%20tool%20that%20Microsoft%20offers%20as%20part%20of%20its%20M365%20suite%20of%20business%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20web%20tab%20M365%20Copilot%20is%20way%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20Microsoft%20Blind%20group%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20M365%20one%20is%20far%20superior%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20productivity%20experiences%20people%20love%20are%20still%20available%20to%20use%20at%20work%20with%20Copilot%20in%20Microsoft%20365%2C%26quot%3B%20Kumar%20wrote%20in%20her%20statement%20to%20BI.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226912235f-40e1-4c4e-99fd-51e934de6645%5C%22%3EUser%20feedback%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20public%20App%20Store%20reviews%2C%20users%20complained%20about%20several%20specific%20issues%20that%20have%20arisen%20since%20the%20consumer%20AI%20Copilot%20app%20was%20updated%20Oct.%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20users%20wrote%20that%20the%20app%20freezes%20or%20is%20slow%20to%20respond.%20Others%20said%20the%20outputs%20seemed%20%26quot%3Bdumber%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20less%20information%20than%20the%20previous%20version.%20Real-time%20information%2C%20such%20as%20sports%20scores%20and%20local%20recommendations%20are%20missing%20now%2C%20or%20the%20app%20just%20says%20%26quot%3BSorry%2C%20I%20can't%20help%20you%20with%20that%26quot%3B%20more%20often%2C%20according%20to%20the%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20also%20complained%20about%20the%20inability%20to%20delete%20old%20conversations.%20Some%20also%20disliked%20changes%20to%20the%20app's%20image%20feature%2C%20which%20previously%20generated%20four%20images%20per%20request%20and%20now%20only%20generates%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e2b2892-58e6-4693-868b-28c5a3ef68ed%5C%22%3EA%20positive%20review%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20positive%20review%20complimented%20the%20app's%20new%20user%20interface%20for%20being%20%26quot%3Bdesigned%20for%20general%20users.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20you%20are%20seeing%20the%20first%20careful%20steps%20in%20this%20direction%20with%20an%20emphasis%20on%20creating%20a%20simpler%2C%20calmer%20experience%20and%20giving%20everyone%20access%20to%20new%20Voice%20capabilities%20that%20unlock%20a%20new%20way%20of%20communicating%20with%20AI%20that's%20much%20more%20natural%2C%20and%20more%20fun%2C%26quot%3B%20Kumar%2C%20the%20Microsoft%20general%20manager%2C%20said%20her%20statement.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20one%20user%20appeared%20unimpressed%20with%20a%20move%20toward%20the%20Copilot%20becoming%20an%20%26quot%3BAI%20companion.%26quot%3B%20This%20was%20an%20approach%20that%20Suleyman%20led%20at%20his%20previous%20startup%2C%20Inflection%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20tries%20to%20be%20my%20friend%20when%20I%20need%20it%20to%20be%20a%20tool%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20user%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20need%20an%20AI%20friend%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BI%20need%20a%20tool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20Microsoft%20employee%20or%20someone%20else%20with%20insight%20to%20share%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EContact%20Ashley%20Stewart%20via%20the%20encrypted%20messaging%20app%20Signal%20(%2B1-425-344-8242)%20or%20email%20(%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aastewart%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eastewart%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%