n%20mind-boggling%20Rs%202%2C36%2C250%20on%20the%20BSE%20in%20just%20one%20trading%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAn%20investment%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20in%20Elcid%20Investments%20shares%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20could%20have%20turned%20into%20Rs%20670%20crore%20after%20the%20price%20surge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20phenomenal%20rise%20has%20propelled%20Elcid%20Investments%20to%20become%20India's%20costliest%20stock%2C%20surpassing%20tyre%20maker%20MRF%20Ltd's%20share%20price%20of%20Rs%201.22%20lakh%20apiece%20(Tuesday%20closing%20price%20on%20the%20BSE).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20astronomical%20increase%20of%2066%2C92%2C535%20percent%C2%A0in%20the%20Elcid%20Investments%20share%20price%20was%20witnessed%20after%20the%20BSE%20auction%20for%20price%20discovery%20of%20holding%20companies.%20Each%20share%20of%20Elcid%20was%20valued%20at%20Rs%202.25%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDuring%20the%20auction%2C%20Elcid's%20shares%20reached%20a%20peak%20traded%20value%20of%20Rs%204.58%20lakh%2C%20although%20the%20price%20discovered%20ultimately%20settled%20at%20Rs%202.25%20lakh%20per%20share.%20However%2C%20the%20stock%20had%20touched%20an%20intraday%20high%20of%20Rs%202%2C36%2C250%20per%20piece%20on%20the%20BSE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBefore%20this%2C%20Elcid%20Investments%20had%20only%20been%20traded%20this%20year%20on%20June%2021%2C%20where%20just%20500%20shares%20changed%20hands%20at%20Rs%203.53%20each.%20In%20July%202024%2C%20Elcid%20Investments%20was%20regarded%20as%20a%20penny%20stock%20worth%20only%20Rs%203.21%20apiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20BSE%20auction%20was%20part%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20improve%20price%20discovery%20for%20investment%20holding%20companies%20(IHCs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20June%202024%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20announced%20a%20new%20initiative%20aimed%20at%20enhancing%20price%20discovery%20for%20Investment%20Companies%20(ICs)%20and%20Investment%20Holding%20Companies%20(IHCs).%20SEBI%20identified%20that%20numerous%20ICs%20and%20IHCs%20were%20trading%20well%20below%20their%20book%20values.%20To%20address%20this%20issue%20and%20ensure%20better%20liquidity%2C%20fair%20pricing%20and%20heightened%20investor%20interest%2C%20SEBI%20introduced%20a%20framework%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cspecial%20call%20auction%20with%20no%20price%20bands%E2%80%9D%2C%20specifically%20for%20these%20stocks.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Elcid%20commenced%20trading%20at%20Rs%202.25%20lakh%20on%20October%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECurrently%20Elcid%20Investment's%20market%20capitalisation%20stands%20at%20Rs%2052%2C010%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730365140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F7n9c9jh8_stock-market-generic_625x300_05_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Felcid-investments-this-small-cap-company-beats-mrf-to-become-indias-costliest-stock-6906927%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20little-known%20smallcap%20stock%20turned%20into%20a%20sensation%20for%20investors%20on%20October%2029.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Felcid-investments-this-small-cap-company-beats-mrf-to-become-indias-costliest-stock-6906927%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20White%20House%20band%20plays%20'Om%20Jai%20Jagdish%20Hare'%20during%20Biden's%20Diwali%20celebration%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730364934000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114812597%2Cimgsize-1123253.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwatch-white-house-band-plays-om-jai-jagdish-hare-during-bidens-diwali-celebration%2Farticleshow%2F114812548.cms