0Of%203rd%20NZ%20Test%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20on%20Thursday%20doesn't%20want%20to%20blame%20the%20batters%20only%20for%20the%20debacle%20against%20the%20visiting%20New%20Zealand%20side%2C%20saying%20that%20every%20player%20has%20the%20responsibility%20towards%20the%20team.%20India%20crashed%20to%20their%20first%20Test%20series%20defeat%20at%20home%20in%2012%20years%20after%20losing%20the%20second%20Test%20by%20113%20runs%20in%20Pune%20on%20October%2026.%20The%20hosts%20had%20lost%20the%20first%20Test%20by%20eight%20wickets%20in%20Bengaluru.%20In%20three%20of%20the%20four%20innings%2C%20the%20team%20totals%20were%2046%2C%20156%20and%20245%20with%20batters%20struggling%20against%20both%20swing%20and%20spin.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20has%20the%20responsibility%2C%20I%20cannot%20say%20just%20the%20batters%20have%20let%20us%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20said%20at%20the%20press%20conference%20ahead%20of%20the%20third%20Test%20from%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20ruled%20out%20bringing%20new%20players%20for%20the%20final%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20can%20think%20of%20that%20(giving%20chance%20to%20players%20who%20have%20not%20played)%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20doused%20the%20speculations%20of%20an%20imminent%20debut%20being%20handed%20to%20Harshit%20Rana%20as%20reported%20in%20some%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHarshit%20Rana%20is%20not%20part%20of%20the%20squad.%20He%20has%20just%20come%20here%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20Australia%20tour%2C%20Abhishek%20(Nayar)%20made%20it%20clear%20yesterday.%20IPL%20retention%20has%20nothing%20to%20be%20spoken%20about%2C%20we%20have%20a%20Test%20match%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20available%20for%20selection%2C%20we%20will%20take%20a%20call%20tomorrow.%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20admitted%20that%20the%20Test%20series%20defeat%20hurt%20the%20team%20but%20said%20it%20should%20spur%20the%20team%20to