%20outcomes%20remain%20uncertain.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Are%20Swing%20States%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSwing%20states%2C%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20battlegrounds%2C%20are%20instrumental%20in%20presidential%20elections.%20They%20are%20characterised%20by%20a%20nearly%20equal%20level%20of%20support%20for%20both%20major%20political%20parties%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20Democrats%20and%20Republicans%2C%20making%20them%20key%20to%20a%20candidate's%20electoral%20strategy.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%202024%2C%20the%20seven%20swing%20states%20are%20Arizona%2C%20Georgia%2C%20Michigan%2C%20Nevada%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Pennsylvania%20and%20Wisconsin.%20These%20regions%20have%20shown%20fluctuating%20voter%20preferences%20in%20recent%20elections.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EArizona%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20Arizona%2C%20where%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20won%20narrowly%20by%20just%2010%2C000%20votes%20in%202020%2C%20immigration%20remains%20a%20hot-button%20issue.%20With%20a%20lengthy%20border%20with%20Mexico%2C%20the%20state's%20voters%20are%20concerned%20about%20immigration%20policies%2C%20a%20topic%20Trump%20has%20vehemently%20criticised%20Harris%20for.%20Abortion%20rights%20have%20also%20been%20a%20bone%20contention%2C%20as%20Republicans%20attempted%20to%20reinstate%20a%20nearly%20total%20ban%20on%20abortions.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EGeorgia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnGeorgia%2C%20another%20state%20where%20Biden%20registered%20a%20victory%20by%20a%20slander%20margin%20of%2013%2C000%20votes%2C%20is%20not%20just%20a%20swing%20state%20but%20also%20a%20legal%20battlefield%20for%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20faces%20allegations%20of%20election%20interference.%20The%20state%20is%20home%20to%20a%20diverse%20demographic%2C%20with%20a%20significant%20African-American%20population%20crucial%20to%20Democratic%20strategies.%20Harris's%20campaign%20aims%20to%20engage%20this%20demographic%20amid%20reports%20of%20growing%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20Biden%20administration.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EMichigan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20Michigan%2C%20where%20Biden%20won%20by%201%2C50%2C000%20votes%2C%20the%20landscape%20is%20complicated%20by%20significant%20discontent%20among%20key%20voter%20groups.%20President%20Biden%20has%20faced%20criticism%20for%20his%20foreign%20policy%2C%20particularly%20on%20US%20military%20aid%20to%20Israel%2C%20which%20has%20bombarded%20Gaza%20for%20over%20a%20year.%20Michigan%20has%20the%20largest%20proportion%20of%20Arab-American%20residents%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20their%20support%20for%20Biden%20has%20become%20increasingly%20tenuous.%20Harris%20has%20shifted%20her%20tone%20vis-a-vis%20Israel%2C%20aiming%20to%20reassure%20voters%20who%20feel%20sidelined%20by%20the%20administration's%20policies%20while%20Trump%20keeps%20firm%20his%20stance%20on%20rapid%20military%20action.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ENevada%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNevada%2C%20traditionally%20a%20Democratic%20stronghold%2C%20shows%20signs%20of%20a%20tightening%20race%2C%20with%20recent%20polls%20suggesting%20a%20shift%20in%20favour%20of%20Republicans.%20Both%20campaigns%20are%20actively%20courting%20Nevada's%20substantial%20Latino%20population%2C%20crucial%20to%20any%20candidate's%20success%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20economic%20recovery%20post-COVID%20has%20been%20sluggish%20in%20Nevada%20compared%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20making%20it%20a%20big%20concern.%20The%20high%20unemployment%20rate%20and%20cost-of-living%20pressures%20are%20also%20key%20issues%20for%20voters%20in%20this%20state.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ENorth%20Carolina%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Donald%20Trump's%20narrow%20victory%20margin%20in%202020%20(by%2074%2C000%20votes)%20has%20made%20this%20state%20a%20toss-up%20for%202024.%20With%20demographics%20and%20issues%20mirroring%20those%20of%20neighbouring%20Georgia%20and%20Arizona%2C%20both%20candidates%20are%20pouring%20resources%20into%20North%20Carolina.%20Trump%20recently%20held%20a%20rally%20here%2C%20promising%20to%20end%20inflation%2C%20stop%20the%20influx%20of%20criminals%20into%20the%20country%20and%20restore%20the%20American%20dream.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EPennsylvania%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnPennsylvania%20holds%2019%20electoral%20votes%20and%20is%20a%20critical%20target%20for%20both%20candidates.%20Biden's%20roots%20in%20Scranton%20give%20him%20a%20personal%20connection%20to%20voters%20in%20this%20working-class%20state.%20The%20economic%20landscape%20has%20shifted%20dramatically%20since%20Biden%20took%20office%2C%20with%20inflation%20affecting%20household%20budgets.%20Recent%20statistics%20show%20that%20grocery%20prices%20in%20Pennsylvania%20have%20risen%20faster%20than%20in%20any%20other%20state%2C%20leading%20to%20significant%20cost-of-living%20pressures%20among%20residents.%20Both%20campaigns%20are%20acutely%20aware%20that%20economic%20issues%20could%20sway%20undecided%20voters%2C%20particularly%20in%20counties%20like%20Erie%2C%20where%20food%20insecurity%20is%20a%20growing%20concern.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWisconsin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFinally%2C%20Wisconsin%20has%20historically%20been%20a%20bellwether%20state%2C%20having%20backed%20the%20winning%20candidate%20in%20the%20last%20two%20elections.%20After%20a%20victory%20with%20just%20over%2021%2C000%20votes%20for%20Biden%20in%202020%2C%20the%20state%20is%20crucial%20for%20both%20the%20candidates.%20There%20is%20a%20growing%20concern%20about%20third-party%20candidates%20potentially%20syphoning%20votes%20away%20from%20the%20main%20candidates.%20Independent%20candidate%20Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr%20suspended%20his%20campaign%20in%20late%20August%20and%20endorsed%20Trump%2C%20which%20could%20alter%20the%20dynamics%20in%20this%20tightly%20contested%20state.%20Democrats%20are%20also%20facing%20challenges%20with%20Green%20Party%20candidate%20Jill%20Stein%2C%20whose%20inclusion%20on%20the%20ballot%20has%20been%20contested.%20Trump%20has%20stressed%20Wisconsin's%20significance%2C%20declaring%20that%20winning%20the%20state%20could%20clinch%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730359920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Foh3m2dlg_donald-trump-kamala-harris_625x300_31_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthe-seven-swing-states-that-could-shape-the-2024-presidential-race-6913487%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20year%2C%20seven%20states%20are%20in%20the%20spotlight%20Arizona%2C%20Georgia%2C%20Michigan%2C%20Nevada%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Pennsylvania%20and%20Wisconsin.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthe-seven-swing-states-that-could-shape-the-2024-presidential-race-6913487%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Vicky-Kat%20celebrated%20Diwali%20with%20family%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730359472000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114809824%2Cimgsize-86364.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthrowback-when-vicky-kaushal-and-katrina-kaif-celebrated-the-festival-of-diwali-with-family%2Farticleshow%2F114809824.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F114809824.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVicky%20Kaushal%20and%20Katrina%20Kaif%20celebrated%20Diwali%20with%20family%2C%20sharing%20festive%20moments%20on%20Instagram.%20Vicky%20expressed%20gratitude%20for%20Katrina%2C%20while%20he%20prepares%20for%20'Chhaava'%20and%20'Love%20and%20War'.%20Katrina%2C%20last%20seen%20in%20'Merry%20Christmas'%2C%20will