ntent%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730357380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FHBT3660_108_comp_BAR_v0021_r709.1024_R.jpeg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236195942%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SPOILER%20WARNING%3A%20This%20story%20includes%20major%20plot%20details%20from%20Episode%208%20and%209%20of%20%E2%80%9CAgatha%20All%20Along%2C%E2%80%9D%20currently%20streaming%20on%20Disney%2B.%20Agatha%20Harkness%2C%20the%20coven-less%20witch%2C%20and%20Billy%20Maximoff%2C%20the%20son%20of%20the%20Scarlet%20Witch%2C%20reached%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Witches%E2%80%99%20Road%20in%20the%20two-part%20finale%20of%20%E2%80%9CAgatha%20All%20Along%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20it%20very%20little%20was%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Adam%20B.%20Vary%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fagatha-all-along-finale-explained-billy-tommy-witches-road-nicholas-scratch-1236195942%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Harshit%20Rana%20Added%20To%20Squad%20For%203rd%20NZ%20Test%3F%20India%20Assistant%20Coach%20Says...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20have%20not%20added%20any%20extra%20player%20to%20their%20squad%20ahead%20of%20the%20third%20Test%20against%20New%20Zealand%20and%20also%20does%20not%20have%20any%20plans%20of%20resting%20pace%20spearhead%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20before%20the%20upcoming%20long%20five-Test%20series%20against%20Australia%20Down%20Under%20starting%20in%20November.%20Amid%20reports%20that%20the%20team%20management%20had%20called%20up%20Harshit%20Rana%20to%20train%20and%20bowl%20for%20the%20team%20ahead%20of%20the%20third%20Test%20against%20New%20Zealand%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%2C%20there%20was%20expectation%20that%20Rana%20could%20be%20added%20to%20the%20squad%20just%20like%20Washington%20Sundar%20was%20called%20up%20just%20before%20the%20second%20Test%20in%20Pune%20as%20the%20Delhi%20medium%20pacer%20is%20one%20of%20the%20bowlers%20picked%20in%20the%20Australia%20tour%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20India's%20assistant%20coach%20Abhishek%20Nayar%20clarified%20that%20not%20extra%20player%20has%20been%20added%20to%20squad%20while%20also%20confirming%20that%20they%20have%20no%20plans%20of%20resting%20Bumrah%20despite%20it%20being%20an%20inconsequential%20Test%20as%20New%20Zealand%20has%20already%20taken%20an%20unassailable%202-0%20lead%20in%20the%20three-match%20series.%20There%20has%20been%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20workload%20of%20Indian%20pacers%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20as%20many%20of%20them%20have%20broken%20down%20even%20during%20a%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20has%20a%20history%20with%20injuries%20and%20thus%20there%20was%20hope%20that%20the%20team%20management%20would%20like%20to%20keep%20him%20fresh%20ahead%20of%20the%20Australia%20series.%20But%20Nayar%20said%20the%20team%20management%20is%20aware%20of%20his%20workload%20but%20feels%20that%20the%20seasoned%20pacer%20from%20Gujarat%20has%20not%20bowled%20too%20many%20overs%20in%20two%20Tests%2C%20which%20incidently%20ended%20prematurely%2C%20thus%20giving%20him%20some%20extra%20rest%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20in%20the%20two%20Test%20matches%20he's%20(Bumrah)%20bowled%20around%2020%2C%2025%20overs.%20So%20he's%20not%20bowled%20a%20lot.%20Yes%2C%20there'll%20always%20be%20a%20thought%20process%20about%20his%20workload.%20Also%2C%20we%20played%20two%20games%20where%20we%20not%20at%205k%20cricket%2C%20it's%20been%20more%20three%2C%20three-and-a-half%20days%2C%20so%20he%20could%20have%20rest.%20But%20Booms%20is%20very%20important%20to%20us%20and%20the%20workload%20will%20always%20be%20something%20on%20our%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Nayar%20said%20in%20a%20pre-match%20press%20conference%20at%20the%20wankhede%20Stadium%20here%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20for%20the%20team%20management%20opting%20against%20resting%20Bumrah%20is%20that%20the%20Wankhede%20pitch%20is%20expected%20to%20help%20seamers%20in%20the%20first%20hour%20or%20so%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20believe%20that%20Wankhede%20will%20always%20give%20pace%20a%20chance%20no%20matter%20what%2C%20especially%20when%20Mumbai%20winter%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20it.%20But%20in%20the%20morning%20there%20will%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20moisture%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20dew%20around.%20So%20you%20will%20expect%20the%20first%20sessions%20to%20have%20a%20bit%20of%20swing.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20of%20the%20pitche%20yet%20because%20it's%20covered%2C%20but%20if%20the%20pitch%20is%20hard%2C%20then%20there%20will%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20swing%20as%20well.%20But%20at%20Wankhede%2C%20you%20will%20always%20see%20fast%20bowlers%20with%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20smile%20on%20their%20face%20in%20the%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nayar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Indian%20team%20needs%20do%20some%20self-reflection%20after%20losing%20a%20home%20series%20in%20more%20than%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirstly%2C%20I%20will%20start%20with%20giving%20a%20lot%20of%20credit%20to%20New%20Zealand%20for%20the%20way%20they%20played%20and%20countered%20spin%20in%20the%20two%20Test%20matches.%20I%20feel%20that%20though%20the%20conditions%20will%20be%20different%20with%20a%20red-soil%20pitch.%20The%20last%20time%20we%20played%20on%20a%20red%20soil%2C%20which%20was%20in%20Chennai%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20guys%20have%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20local%20cricketers%20and%20they%20understand%20what%20these%20conditions%20are%20and%20how%20the%20pitch%20is%20going%20to%20pan%20out.%20I%20think%20it's%20more%20about%2C%20at%20this%20level%2C%20self%20reflection%20for%20every%20player%20to%20go%20in%20and%20understand%20their%20game%20plans%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20for%20us%2C%20it's%20more%20about%20self%20reflection%20and%20what%20we%20can%20do%20as%20a%20team.%20There's%20always%20advantages%2C%20but%20I%20always%20believe%20that%20what%20you've%20done%20in%20the%20past%20doesn't%20really%20matter%20in%20the%20present.%20It's%20about%20how%20you%20turn%20up%20on%20that%20particular%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730357280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Ftuup79k_harshit-rana_625x300_12_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fharshit-rana-added-to-squad-for-3rd-new-zealand-test-india-assistant-coach-clears-air-6908142%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20assistant%20coach%20Abhishek%20Nayar%20on%20Wednesday%20cleared%20air%20on%20reports%20of%20Harshit%20Rana%20being%20added%20to%20the%20squad%20for%20the%20third%20Test%20match%20against%20New%20Zealand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fharshit-rana-added-to-squad-for-3rd-new-zealand-test-india-assistant-coach-clears-air-6908142%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Squid%20Game%20S2%20scene%20leaked%20ahead%20of%20teaser%20release%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730356855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114807900%2Cimgsize-18056.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fsquid-game-season-2-scene-leaks-online-ahead-of-teaser-release-watch%2Farticleshow%2F114806965.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F114806965.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENetflix%20has%20announced%20the%20release%20of%20a%20new%20teaser%20for%20Squid%20Game%20Season%202%20on%20November%201.%20A%20leaked%20scene%20reportedly%20shows%20players%20navigating%20a%20giant%20merry-go-round%20surrounded%20by%20colorful%20doors.%20The%20new%20season%20will%20feature%20familiar%20characters%20like%20Seong%20Gi-hun%20and%20delve%20deeper%20into%20the%20deadly%20games%E2%80%99%20organization.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fsquid-game-season-2-scene-leaks-online-ahead-of-teaser-release-watch%2Farticleshow%2F114806965.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Invictus%20Games%20CEO%20Reveals%20How%20Meghan%20Markle%20Is%20To%20Be%20Addressed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMeghan%20Markle%20insists%20on%20being%20addressed%20as%20%E2%80%9CMa'am%2C%E2%80%9D%20Invictus%20Games%20CEO%20Scott%20Moore%20has%20revealed.%20The%20newly%20appointed%20head%20of%20the%20Invictus%20Games%20Vancouver%20Whistler%202025%20disclosed%20that%20he%20was%20briefed%20on%20this%20unique%20approach%20before%20his%20first%20encounter%20with%20the%20Duchess%20of%20Sussex%20during%20their%20visit%20to%20Canada%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20make%20sure%20to%20ask%20how%20I%20should%20be%20addressing%20them%20when%20they%20get%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Moore%20shared%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2F3am%2Fus-celebrity-news%2Fhow-meghan-markle-must-addressed-33997418%5C%22%3EThe%20Mirror%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20advice%20he%20received%20was%3A%20a%20simple%20%E2%80%9CMa'am%E2%80%9D%20for%20Meghan%20and%20%E2%80%9CSir%E2%80%9D%20for%20Prince%20Harry.%20This%20guideline%20differs%20from%20the%20formal%20address%20typically%20reserved%20for%20royals%2C%20where%20they%20are%20addressed%20first%20as%20%E2%80%9CYour%20Royal%20Highness%E2%80%9D%20followed%20by%20%E2%80%9CMa'am%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9CSir.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20after%20stepping%20back%20from%20royal%20duties%20in%202020%2C%20the%20Duke%20and%20Duchess%20of%20Sussex%20no%20longer%20hold%20%E2%80%9CHRH%E2%80%9D%20titles%2C%20making%20this%20protocol%20unnecessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20to%20maintain%20formal%20titles%20is%20different%20from%20Prince%20Harry's%20previous%20stance%20on%20informality.%20In%202020%2C%20he%20attended%20a%20tourism%20conference%20in%20Edinburgh%2C%20where%20he%20told%20the%20host%20and%20the%20audience%20to%20simply%20call%20him%20%E2%80%9CHarry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Invictus%20Games%20is%20an%20international%20multi-sport%20event%20for%20wounded%2C%20injured%20and%20sick%20servicemen%20and%20women%2C%20both%20active%20and%20veteran.%20The%20Games%20were%20founded%20by%20Prince%20Harry%20in%202014%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20Warrior%20Games%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20ex-royal%20couple's%20February%20trip%20to%20Vancouver%2C%20the%20Sussexes%20took%20time%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20Invictus%20community%20on%20Valentine's%20Day%2C%20joining%20participants%20for%20winter%20sports%20training.%20This%20event%2C%20named%20the%20%E2%80%9COne%20Year%20to%20Go%E2%80%9D%20celebration%2C%20spanned%20three%20days%20and%20allowed%20members%20of%20the%20international%20Invictus%20community%20to%20participate%20in%20various%20winter%20sports%20in%20preparation%20for%20next%20year's%20games.%20The%20Vancouver%20event%2C%20which%20will%20take%20place%20from%20February%208%20to%20February%2016%2C%202025%2C%20will%20build%20on%20the%20success%20of%20the%202023%20games%20held%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20last%20year's%20games%2C%20Meghan%20Markle%20hinted%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20bringing%20along%20their%20children%2C%20Prince%20Archie%20and%20Princess%20Lilibet.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730355960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ffv3rifoc_meghan-markle_625x300_01_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finvictus-games-ceo-reveals-how-meghan-markle-is-to-be-addressed-6912815%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meghan%20Markle%20insists%20on%20being%20addressed%20as%20%26quot%3BMa'am%2C%26quot%3B%20Invictus%20Games%20CEO%20Scott%20Moore%20has%20revealed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finvictus-games-ceo-reveals-how-meghan-markle-is-to-be-addressed-6912815%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHorrible%20Scene%26quot%3B%3A%20Suspected%20Gang's%20Wild%20Bash%20Leaves%20Airbnb%20In%20Ruins%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20homeowner%20in%20a%20Colorado%20mountain%20town%20found%20her%20Airbnb%20rental%20in%20ruins%20after%20a%20chaotic%20party%20allegedly%20hosted%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Tren%20de%20Aragua%20gang.%20Karen%20Martiz%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20property%20in%20Evergreen%20%E2%80%94%20around%2048%20km%20west%20of%20Denver%20%E2%80%94%20reported%20damages%20amounting%20to%20%2416%2C000%20(around%20Rs%2013.45%20lakh).%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20wild%20bash%2C%20Ms%20Martiz%20found%20a%20scene%20of%20utter%20disarray%2C%20with%20cigarette%20butts%20scattered%20about%2C%20chewing%20gum%20smeared%20across%20carpets%2C%20walls%20and%20ceilings%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20empty%20alcohol%20bottles%20alongside%20drug%20paraphernalia.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMs%20Martiz%20is%20convinced%20the%20mess%20was%20the%20result%20of%20the%20Venezuelan%20prison%20gang's%20activities.%20The%20local%20law%20enforcement%20agency%2C%20the%20Clear%20Creek%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%2C%20supports%20this%20claim%2C%20saying%20they%20suspected%20members%20of%20Tren%20de%20Aragua%20were%20part%20of%20the%20large%20group%20of%2080%20to%20100%20individuals%20who%20partied%20at%20the%20Airbnb.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CI%20have%20put%20all%20my%20energy%20and%20love%20into%20this%20property%20to%20make%20it%20beautiful%20for%20my%20guests.%20It's%20a%20beautiful%20place.%20Everybody%20loved%20it.%20We%20have%20been%20hosting%20for%20two%20years%20and%20this%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20I%20showed%20up%20here%20and%20my%20house%20was%20completely%20destroyed.%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ms%20Martiz%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fcolorado-airbnb-host-faces-16k-damages-after-suspected-migrant-gang-members-destroy-property%5C%22%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMartiz%20described%20entering%20her%20home%20after%20the%20guests'%20departure%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Chorrible%20scene%2C%E2%80%9D%20expressing%20disbelief%20over%20the%20level%20of%20destruction.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20walked%20into%20my%20house%2C%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20I%20was%20actually%20living%20this.%20Because%20until%20you%20live%20it%2C%20you%20are%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98Is%20this%20even%20something%20that%20could%20happen%20to%20people%3F'%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Tren%20de%20Aragua%20gang's%20activities%20have%20been%20reported%20across%20states%2C%20including%20Aurora%2C%20Colorado%2C%20where%20they%20have%20taken%20control%20of%20multiple%20apartment%20complexes%20and%20committed%20violent%20crimes%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F09%2F12%2Fus-news%2Finside-the-migrant-gang-warzone-of-aurora-colorado%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CIt's%20very%20real%2C%20and%20this%20group%20of%20people%20(Tren%20de%20Aragua)%20are%20doing%20it%20to%20people%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ms%20Martiz%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20New%20York%20Post%20has%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20reported%20on%20the%20Tren%20de%20Aragua%20gang's%20infiltration%20into%20the%20Denver%20suburb%2C%20detailing%20how%20the%20gang%20took%20over%20multiple%20neglected%20apartment%20complexes%2C%20with%20their%20regional%20leader%2C%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Cookie%2C'%20implicated%20in%20violent%20crimes.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20problem%20garnered%20national%20attention%2C%20notably%20from%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20visited%20Aurora%20earlier%20in%20October%20for%20a%20rally.%20He%20announced%20his%20intention%20to%20invoke%20a%20226-year-old%20law%20aimed%20at%20dismantling%20Tren%20de%20Aragua%20and%20deporting%20its%20members.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTrump%20told%20supporters%20at%20the%20rally%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20rescue%20Aurora%20and%20every%20town%20that%20has%20been%20invaded%20and%20conquered%2C%E2%80%9D%20emphasising%20his%20administration's%20commitment%20to%20either%20imprisoning%20or%20expelling%20these%20%E2%80%9Cvicious%20and%20bloodthirsty%20criminals.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMs%20Martiz%20agrees%20with%20Trump's%20assessment%20of%20the%20gang's%20menace%20to%20society.%20%E2%80%9CAbsolutely%20no%20exaggeration%20at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20people%20are%20not%20here%20to%20do%20good.%20They%20have%20nothing%20to%20lose.%20They%20don't%20care.%20They're%20just%20coming%20in%2C%20destroying%20properties%2C%20people's%20lives%20like%20nothing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730355960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F936gfbcg_airbnb_625x300_31_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsuspected-gang-s-wild-bash-leaves-airbnb-in-ruins-owner-reports-rs-13-45-lakh-in-damages-6912805%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Airbnb%20owner%20found%20cigarette%20butts%2C%20chewing%20gum%20on%20surfaces%20and%20hundreds%20of%20empty%20alcohol%20bottles%20and%20drug%20paraphernalia%20scattered%20everywhere.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canoni