0Reuters.%20It%20included%20sanctions%20on%20dozens%20of%20Chinese%2C%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20Indian%20companies%2C%20the%20most%20from%20those%20countries%20to%20be%20hit%20in%20one%20package%20so%20far%2C%20according%20to%20the%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20hit%20with%20sanctions%20were%20targets%20in%20Russia%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20Turkey%2C%20Thailand%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20Switzerland%20and%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20comes%20as%20Washington%20has%20sought%20to%20curb%20Russia's%20evasion%20of%20the%20sanctions%20imposed%20after%20its%202022%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20has%20killed%20or%20wounded%20thousands%20and%20reduced%20cities%20to%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20should%20send%20a%20serious%20message%20to%20both%20the%20governments%20and%20the%20private%20sectors%20of%20these%20countries%20that%20the%20U.S.%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20countering%20the%20evasion%20of%20our%20sanctions%20against%20Russia%20and%20to%20continue%20putting%20pressure%20on%20Russia%20to%20end%20its%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20official%2C%20speaking%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20U.S.%20Treasury%20Department%20imposed%20sanctions%20on%20274%20targets%2C%20while%20the%20State%20Department%20designated%20more%20than%20120%20and%20the%20Commerce%20Department%20added%2040%20companies%20and%20research%20institutions%20to%20a%20trade%20restriction%20list%20over%20their%20alleged%20support%20of%20the%20Russian%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20and%20our%20allies%20will%20continue%20to%20take%20decisive%20action%20across%20the%20globe%20to%20stop%20the%20flow%20of%20critical%20tools%20and%20technologies%20that%20Russia%20needs%20to%20wage%20its%20illegal%20and%20immoral%20war%20against%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20Deputy%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Wally%20Adeyemo%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20Washington%20embassy%20spokesperson%20Liu%20Pengyu%20said%20Beijing%20was%20firmly%20opposed%20to%20%26quot%3Billegal%20and%20unjustifiable%20unilateral%20sanctions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20U.S.%20makes%20false%20accusations%20against%20China's%20normal%20trade%20with%20Russia%2C%20just%20as%20it%20continues%20to%20pour%20unprecedented%20military%20aid%20into%20Ukraine.%20This%20is%20typical%20double%20standard%2C%20and%20extremely%20hypocritical%20and%20irresponsible%2C%26quot%3B%20Liu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20and%20Indian%20embassies%20in%20Washington%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%20Turkey's%20government%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20U.S.%20has%20repeatedly%20warned%20against%20supplying%20Russia%20with%20Common%20High%20Priority%20Items%20-%20advanced%20components%20including%20microelectronics%20deemed%20by%20the%20U.S.%20and%20European%20Union%20as%20likely%20to%20be%20used%20for%20Russia's%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Department%20official%20said%20there%20has%20been%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20export%20of%20such%20goods%20from%20India%20to%20Russia%2C%20as%20well%20as%20increased%20interest%20in%20taking%20action%20against%20the%20companies%20facilitating%20such%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20administration%20official%20said%20Wednesday's%20action%20was%20designed%20to%20signal%20the%20U.S.%20would%20take%20action%20against%20Indian%20companies%20if%20progress%20is%20not%20made%20through%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20India%2C%20we%20have%20been%20very%20direct%20and%20blunt%20with%20them%20about%20the%20concerns%20we%20have%20about%20what%20we%20see%20as%20sort%20of%20emerging%20trends%20in%20that%20country%20that%20we%20want%20to%20stop%20before%20they%20get%20too%20far%20down%20the%20road%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20official%2C%20speaking%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia-based%20Futrevo%20was%20among%20the%20companies%20targeted%20by%20the%20State%20Department%2C%20which%20accused%20it%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20supply%20of%20high-priority%20items%20to%20the%20Russia-based%20manufacturer%20of%20Orlan%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Treasury%20also%20targeted%20Shreya%20Life%20Sciences%20Private%20Limited%2C%20which%20it%20said%20since%202023%20has%20sent%20hundreds%20of%20shipments%20of%20U.S.-trademarked%20technology%20to%20Russia%2C%20totaling%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECHINA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20senior%20State%20Department%20official%20told%20Reuters%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20more%20than%2070%25%20of%20the%20high-priority%20goods%20getting%20to%20Russia%20was%20from%20China%2C%20more%20than%20an%20estimated%20%2422%20billion%20worth%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20over%2013%20times%20the%20next%20largest%20supplier%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said%2C%20which%20as%20of%20the%20end%20of%202023%20was%20Turkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20targeted%20on%20Wednesday%20were%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20China-based%20companies%20involved%20in%20the%20shipment%20of%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20worth%20of%20high-priority%20items%20to%20Russia-based%20companies%20or%20end-users%2C%20the%20State%20and%20Treasury%20departments%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20U.S.%20also%20took%20actions%20on%20a%20variety%20of%20entities%20supporting%20Russia's%20Arctic%20LNG%202%20project%2C%20which%20is%2060%25%20owned%20by%20Russia's%20Novatek%2C%20and%20was%20to%20become%20Russia's%20largest%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%20plant.%20Novatek%20has%20been%20forced%20to%20scale%20back%20Arctic%20LNG%202%2C%20which%20had%20been%20planned%20to%20reach%20an%20eventual%20output%20of%2019.8%20million%20metric%20tons%20per%20year%2C%20following%20a%20raft%20of%2