you%20respect%20a%20man%20who%20is%20not%20getting%20up%20and%20going%20to%20work%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%20It%E2%80%99s%20time%20we%20start%20respecting%20men%20who%20embrace%20their%20weaknesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20Images%20Courtesy%20Nikhil%20Taneja%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730126019000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-28-at-19.40.08-min-1730124705.jpeg%3Fw%3D1067%26quality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D372684%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nikhil%20Taneja%2C%20founder%20of%20Yuvaa%2C%20a%20youth%20media%20company%2C%20went%20through%20a%20period%20of%20great%20anxiety%20when%20he%20was%20doing%20well%20in%20his%20career.%20This%20led%20him%20to%20take%20a%20break%20and%20look%20at%20what%20success%20really%20means%2C%20breaking%20out%20of%20the%20definitions%20of%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20a%20man%2C%20and%20the%20roles%20defined%20by%20society.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F372684%2Fnikhil-taneja-yuvaa-mens-mental-health-advocate-yuvaa-clinical-anxiety-yrf-producer-writer-be-a-man%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Transforming%20Lives%3A%20How%20a%20Mumbai-Based%20Initiative%20Has%20Delivered%20Quality%20Healthcare%20Since%201968%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EL%26amp%3BT%20Health%20Centre%2C%20Andheri%2C%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshok%20Tukaram%20Pawar%20(73)%20is%20eager%20for%20his%20appointment%20slated%20for%20this%20afternoon%20with%20his%20physician%2C%20Padma%20Shri%20awardee%20Dr%20Alaka%20Deshpande.%20It%20is%20a%20weekday%2C%20but%20the%20OPD%20%E2%80%94%20where%20Pawar%20is%20waiting%20with%20the%20other%20patients%2C%20also%20here%20to%20see%20Dr%20Deshpande%20%E2%80%94%20is%2