I%20live%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reflects%2C%20her%20identity%20deeply%20intertwined%20with%20her%20mission.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Jawai%E2%80%99s%20concerns%20has%20been%20the%20alarming%20decline%20of%20native%20flora%20and%20fauna%2C%20including%20the%20Indian%20Bustard%2C%20with%20only%20a%20couple%20of%20hundred%20remaining%2C%20and%20a%20staggering%2060%25%20drop%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F364022%2Fcamel-charisma-milk-sadri-rajasthan-kumbalgarh-dairy-paper-wool-cheese%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecamel%20populations%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%201995.%20Padmaja%20understood%20early%20on%20that%20addressing%20these%20critical%20issues%20required%20a%20multifaceted%20approach%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20not%20only%20conserved%20wildlife%20but%20also%20restored%20entire%20ecosystems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHealing%20the%20land%20through%20collaboration%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grasslands%2C%20once%20overrun%20with%20invasive%20plants%2C%20were%20replanted%20with%20native%20species.%20The%20region%E2%80%99s%20revival%20included%20the%20reintroduction%20of%20crucial%20native%20plants%20like%20Rohida%2C%20the%20state%20plant%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20known%20for%20its%20healing%20properties%20and%20federally%20protected%20from%20cutting.%20Other%20plants%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3EPalaash%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20natural%20mosquito%20repellent%2C%20and%20medicinal%20trees%20like%20Kumatiyo%20and%20neem%20were%20also%20replanted%20to%20restore%20the%20land%E2%80%99s%20balance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20efforts%20are%20not%20about%20human%20intervention%20for%20intervention%E2%80%99s%20sake%2C%20but%20rather%20about%20allowing%20nature%20to%20heal%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises%2C%20with%20human%20involvement%20only%20when%20absolutely%20necessary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20approach%20lies%20a%20collaborative%20spirit.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20comes%20when%20you%E2%80%99re%20alone%2C%E2%80%9D%20Padmaja%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20when%20you%20start%20talking%20to%20people%2C%20they%20might%20think%20you%E2%80%99re%20mad%20for%20taking%20on%20something%20like%20this.%20Yet%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20others%20just%20as%20mad%2C%20if%20not%20more%2C%20ready%20to%20help%20you%20realise%20a%20dream.%E2%80%9D%20This%20sentiment%20of%20shared%20responsibility%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20Raika%20community%E2%80%99s%20brave%20stance%20during%20the%20Godwar%20Chipko%20Movement%2C%20where%20they%20opposed%20the%20mining%20lobby%20in%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%94%20an%20act%20of%20defiance%20in%20a%20region%20where%20such%20resistance%20is%20rare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20also%20focuses%20on%20the%20preservation%20of%20the%20Indian%20Sloth%20Bears%20and%20hyenas%20by%20practising%20safe%20tourism%20activities%20along%20with%20replantation%20to%20help%20maintain%20their%20habitat.%20Leopards%2C%20the%20only%20big%20cat%20to%20survive%20the%20savannah%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20standing%20on%20what%20Padmaja%20calls%20the%20%E2%80%9Clast%20green%20western%20frontier%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20are%20worshipped%20by%20the%20locals.%20%E2%80%9CMan%20needs%20to%20respect%20the%20wild%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20asserts%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbecause%20nature%20knows%20nothing%20but%20respect.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-blo